marion labs <mkc> votes split, dividend hike
    kansas city, mo., march 16 - 
marion laboratories inc said its board declared a two-for-one common
stock split in the form of a dividend, with distribution april 21,
record march 25. the board also said it intends to increase the
regular quarterly dividend by 43 pct, to five cts a share, reflecting
the split. it said the increase will be declared at the may 1987 board
meeting and reflected in regular payments beginning in july 1987.
